      "html": "<div class=\"mySlides fade\">\n<style>\n.uac-wrap{display:flex;height:calc(100vh - 80px);background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1a2e 0%,#16213e 100%);overflow:hidden;}\n.uac-left{flex:1;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:20px;position:relative;}\n.uac-left img{max-height:80vh;max-width:100%;border-radius:12px;box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);}\n.uac-right{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:40px 48px;direction:rtl;text-align:right;gap:20px;}\n.uac-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#f6a67e22;border:1px solid #f6a67e55;color:#f6a67e;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:50px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;width:fit-content;}\n.uac-title{font-size:clamp(22px,2.5vw,32px);font-weight:900;color:white;line-height:1.3;}\n.uac-title span{color:#f6a67e;}\n.uac-explain{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:16px;padding:20px 24px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;}\n.uac-point{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;color:#ffffffcc;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;}\n.uac-point-icon{flex-shrink:0;width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:14px;}\n.uac-point-green{background:rgba(76,175,80,0.2);color:#66bb6a;}\n.uac-point-blue{background:rgba(30,95,116,0.3);color:#5b8fa8;}\n.uac-bottom{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:rgba(246,166,126,0.15);border:1.5px solid rgba(246,166,126,0.4);padding:12px 18px;border-radius:12px;cursor:pointer;transition:background 0.2s;}\n.uac-bottom:hover{background:rgba(246,166,126,0.25);}\n.uac-bottom-text{color:#f6a67e;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;}\n.uac-bottom-arrow{flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;}\n@media(max-width:900px){.uac-wrap{flex-direction:column;}.uac-left{max-height:40vh;}.uac-right{padding:20px;}}\n</style>\n<div class=\"uac-wrap\">\n  <div class=\"uac-left\">\n    <div style=\"position:relative;display:inline-block;\">\n      <img src=\".//images//How_to_download_and_install_Everything_search_tool_from_voidtools_and_set_it_up_on_Windows_9.png\" alt=\"בקרת חשבון משתמש\">\n      \n      <div class=\"box\" style=\"top:85.5%;left:50.5%;right:5.5%;bottom:5.2%;cursor:pointer;\" onclick=\"nextSlide()\"></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"uac-right\">\n    <div class=\"uac-badge\">\n      <svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#f6a67e\" stroke=\"none\"><path d=\"M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z\"/></svg>\n      זה בסדר גמור!\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"uac-title\">קופץ לכם <span>חלון כזה?</span><br>אל תפחדו - זה נורמלי.</div>\n    <div class=\"uac-explain\">\n      <div class=\"uac-point\">\n        <div class=\"uac-point-icon uac-point-blue\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#5b8fa8\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"/></svg></div>\n        <div><b style=\"color:white;\">זה וינדוס ששומר עליכם</b> - כשמתקינים תוכנה, וינדוס לפעמים בודק שאתם מסכימים. זה סימן שהמחשב שומר עליכם.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"uac-point\">\n        <div class=\"uac-point-icon uac-point-green\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#66bb6a\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"/></svg></div>\n        <div><b style=\"color:white;\">התוכנה בטוחה</b> - הורדתם אותה מהאתר הרשמי, ממש בשלב הקודם. אין סיבה לדאגה.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"uac-point\">\n        <div class=\"uac-point-icon uac-point-blue\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#5b8fa8\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"23 4 23 10 17 10\"/><polyline points=\"1 20 1 14 7 14\"/><path d=\"M3.51 9a9 9 0 0114.85-3.36L23 10M1 14l4.64 4.36A9 9 0 0020.49 15\"/></svg></div>\n        <div><b style=\"color:white;\">יכול לקפוץ יותר מפעם אחת</b> - החלון הזה עשוי לקפוץ גם כמה פעמים במהלך ההתקנה. בכל פעם שהוא קופץ, לחצו \"כן\".</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"uac-bottom\" onclick=\"nextSlide()\">\n      <div class=\"uac-bottom-arrow\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#66bb6a\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"/></svg></div>\n      <div class=\"uac-bottom-text\">בכל פעם שהחלון קופץ - לחצו \"כן\"</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>"
